ghost-role-information-grimalkin-name = Grimalkin
ghost-role-information-grimalkin-description = You are a Grimalkin, a small, friendly, cat-like noospheric spirit called forth by a kind offering.
ghost-role-information-grimalkin-rules = Assist your summoner with small tasks and keep their morale up! Use your pouch to carry small objects for them, or just a small bit of shinies you find around. Be kind to other living things, but try to be rid of pests as nicely as you can.
